Root Level State Management Provider Folder
--------------------------------------------
  - Providers found here are global in the sense that they can be found throughout the codebase
  - These providers differ from local controller providers in that local controllers shall be autodisposed when local screen is disposed
  - These providers persist across screens and are not disposed of unless the application is closed

Available State Management Providers
-------------------------------------
 - Dark Mode Provider - Handles Toggling Application Theme Light/Dark Mode
 - Data Provider
 ....- Navigation Bar Provider - Handles Moving Between Bottom Nav Bar Pages
 